variables.name: ITSD_Emergency_System_Announcement
variables.description: Emergency System Announcement for Employee Entry Point
variables.value: Thank you for calling the Erickson Senior Living IT Service Desk  -  At this time we are aware of the Kansas City Chiefs win over the San Francisco 49ers  - Please console your 49er friends who are fans

promptsTts.value:
<speak>
Please stay on the line and your call will be answered in the order it was received.
All agents are currently assisting other clients and we will be with you as soon as possible.
Thank you.
You are the <say-as interpret-as="ordinal"> {{ q_position }} </say-as> call in queue.
</speak>

We apologize for the continued delay, but we are experiencing a heavy call volume, we encourage you to use our Courtesy Call Back Option by pressing one. 
Courtesy call back allows you to receive a call back from the IT Service Desk without 
losing your place in the queue, or you may continue to hold and you call will be answered 
in the order it was received

properties.name: SetVariable_jys
properties.description: callback_queue variable is mapped between flows. Ensures caller remains in the same queue when be queued for callback
If pressing an invalid 0-9 option play message and send back to q

properties.description: get queue information to determine logged on agents

properties.description: condition to check if agents logged

properties.name: SetVariable_ghv
properties.description: take +e164 DNIS and make 10 digit. Used for variable audio file

properties.name: SetVariable_zrh
properties.description: set callback ani based of DNIS. Passed to callback flow

properties.name: BlindTransfer_0gc
properties.description: transfer to vm. Diversion Header from transfer is used to find the vm
